Specify a target location in which to search for source files of a specified type. Found source files are combined into a single PDF-file.

Usage: src2pdf <src-loc> <file-type1,file-type2,...> <out-file>
Example: src2pdf ~/git/c-proj c,h ~/git/c-proj/doc -T4 --columns=1
Default a2ps layout: a2ps --columns=2 -T3 -q
